{"tid":2093112,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"龜龜仲有冇得救？","createTime":"2020-07-03T15:28:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T12:59:29.000Z","uid":89442,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"9c694ae6bbe5229e67f07aa357e93bf9a412da62","tid":2093112,"uid":89442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />養咗十幾年啦 有啲咩三七廿一都好唔捨得<br />\n聽朝book醫生睇 <br />\n一見到佢個樣就覺得心痛<br />\n大家有冇試過類似情況？<br />\n同埋佢冇食嘢好耐啦 屙嘅屎都唔係屎 似黏液多啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jkus55g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJkus55g.png&h=b9ec5304&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u1K48iH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu1K48iH.png&h=34de524f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fg6nUYO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffg6nUYO.png&h=a77be0e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"218d2e97ddcf004b100145a3e47564a8db17f25a","tid":2093112,"uid":89442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:28:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"96efeac6512283c0d6e5e5ded2f7d357271a86dd","tid":2093112,"uid":89442,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:29:10.000Z","msg":"見醫生前我有咩可以做住先？"},{"pid":"fb84486f8ef4a7f934897f53417e24280bf46ff5","tid":2093112,"uid":89442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:29:55.000Z","msg":"有冇人有養烏龜架？"},{"pid":"d0a4174624ff696388acd991ce9082012a77e67f","tid":2093112,"uid":89442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:30:11.000Z","msg":"點解冇人嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe328f18a862dbf21b8d552de1dce0cae06f975","tid":2093112,"uid":89442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:30:50.000Z","msg":"pus