ke":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1cd772bcfa2135f89e8a2480e96797c1c3f48847","tid":2093112,"uid":89442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfe743da80b04127cda0d07d3b09391fc43d7145","tid":2093112,"uid":2114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"784015f52f06c812504a2e680b6730238073c412","tid":2093112,"uid":89442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T03:53:31.000Z","msg":"唔該你 咁我盡量收集"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T03:54:16.000Z","msg":"另外其實你book 咗獸醫未㗎<br />\n啲appointment 好鬼full <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T03:55:24.000Z","msg":"我book咗啦 full到要7號先有 <br />\nbook咗荃灣楊醫生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T04:01:29.000Z","msg":"如果到7 號先有<br />\n我教你以下方法<br />\n係荃灣享和黃醫生教我洗傷口嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n1. 棉花棒點 hibitane (chlorhexidine), 先係傷口抺一次。hibitane 可以藥房買到，粉紅色一包包<br />\n2. 等一陣俾hibitane 發揮消毒作用<br />\n3. 之後用生理鹽水 (normal saline) 沖一沖，一樣藥房買到<br />\n4. 最後揸抗生素Silver sulphadiazine cream, 等15分鐘之後先俾佢落返水<br />\n<br />\nSSD cream 係人度用係燙傷膏嚟<br />\n我睇龜嘅醫書講佢係好常用嘅broad spectrum antibiotics<br />\n所以可以放心使用<br />\n藥房應該有賣，但唔知佢肯唔肯賣俾你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4683282e4f9cb4aa07d39274d6e95fb92df23f4f","tid":2093112,"uid":89442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d586b9d85db8f681a9793a010d1dbdee3a40513f","tid":2093112,"uid":2114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1cd772bcfa2135f89e8a2480e96797c1c3f48847","tid":2093112,"uid":89442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfe743da80b04127cda0d07d3b09391fc43d7145","tid":2093112,"uid":2114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T03:54:16.000Z","msg":"另外其實你book 咗獸醫未㗎<br />\n啲appointment 好鬼full <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T03:55:24.000Z","msg":"我book咗啦 full到要7號先有 <br />\nbook咗荃灣楊醫生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T04:01:29.000Z","msg":"如果到7 號先有<br />\n我